1NT 2D pass 2H pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 1, chOption: N, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 0, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "e614c2b0ce4732d5dc6d864088625a769da784e7168be76e9a781dbbf9017946"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{With 10 HCP and 10 red cards you have a good enough hand for an immediate DONT bid. So you bid 2\D, promising that suit and a Major.

Partner responds 2\H.  

Don't get carried away, partner isn't really bidding a \H suit as much as he is letting you know he doesn't like \Ds. You were only competing for a partscore and here you are in a partscore. You pass.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "2"]
[Dealer "N"]
[Vulnerable "NS"]
[Deal "N:K7.Q75.KQT4.AQT2 A92.AKJT63.73.65 QJT83.4.J92.KJ84 654.982.A865.973"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "2H"]
